c: 3
v: 47
t: "Maryam tama caagid Qajibsitak itteh;yi-Rabbow Baxa geyam mannal yoh takkee? Seehadayti digibih yol maxayyoowinnaay anu dalweyna hinniyok itte, malaykatti (jibriil kinnuk) teetik iyyeh, Nabâ Yallih caagid tamannaay usuk isih faxam gina, usuk caagiidak caagidik teyna meklaah ginam faxa waqdi, toysa cagalah woo hiimik tik iyyaah edde takke iyye"